# Game file backup before edits

Before changing any file inside the installed game directory (e.g. `C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Sovereign Syndicate\`), always:

1. Create backup under `C:\Temp\SovereignSyndicateBackup\`
2. Use timestamp in filename: `SyndicateLocalization_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.csv` (or matching extension)
3. Confirm backup path in the response before/after editing
4. Never edit game files without a fresh backup in the same session
5. **Also** follow `no-game-update-without-permission.mdc`: no game writes unless the user explicitly allows deploy/update in that turn

Restore from backup if the user asks to roll back.
